### Top 2000 Songs API Tests

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7003/api

### 1. Get first page of songs (default page size 50)
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get second page of songs
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs?page=2&pageSize=50
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get songs with custom page size (25 songs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs?page=1&pageSize=25
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get song by title (Bohemian Rhapsody)
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs/by-title/bohemian-rhapsody
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get song by title (Hotel California)
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs/by-title/hotel-california
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get song by title with spaces (exact title)
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs/by-title/Bohemian%20Rhapsody
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Get song by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Get song history by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs/1/history
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Test pagination - last page (assuming 2000 songs, 50 per page = 40 pages)
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs?page=40&pageSize=50
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Test invalid page (should return empty or error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs?page=999&pageSize=50
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Test page size validation (max 100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs?page=1&pageSize=150
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. Get song that doesn't exist
GET {{baseUrl}}/songs/by-title/this-song-does-not-exist
Content-Type: application/json

